## Executive Overview

The STARFORCE GRID represents the first large-scale operational networking architecture designed to unify all major PI220 systems into a coordinated communications, telemetry, command, and intelligence ecosystem.

While previous platforms focused on individual vehicle intelligence, STARFORCE GRID focuses on collective intelligence.

The system establishes a persistent network capable of linking:

* PI220 CORE
* NEO CORE NODE
* X2M
* STARFRAME
* AFAT
* APHEX-X1
* Boeing 220-X
* Boeing 220-Y
* Boeing 220-G platforms

into a unified operational environment.

The central philosophy is:

> One aircraft can be intelligent.

> A network of intelligent aircraft becomes an ecosystem.

