## Technical Assessment

STARFORCE GRID is a distributed communications, telemetry, command, and intelligence architecture designed to interconnect PI220 aerospace systems into a unified operational network. By integrating PI220 CORE, NEO CORE NODE, X2M, STARFRAME, AFAT, APHEX-X1, and Boeing 220-family platforms, it establishes the foundation for persistent aerospace coordination and distributed mission intelligence.

